{"thi-ap27:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap27:0.2":"Kundalakesivagga ","thi-ap27:0.3":"Bhaddakapilanitheriapadana ","thi-ap27:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","thi-ap27:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","thi-ap27:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","thi-ap27:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","thi-ap27:2.1":"Tadahu hamsavatiyam, ","thi-ap27:2.2":"videho nama namato; ","thi-ap27:2.3":"Setthi pahutaratano, ","thi-ap27:2.4":"tassa jaya ahosaham. ","thi-ap27:3.1":"Kadaci so naradiccam, ","thi-ap27:3.2":"Upecca saparijjano; ","thi-ap27:3.3":"Dhammamassosi buddhassa, ","thi-ap27:3.4":"Sabbadukkhabhayappaham. ","thi-ap27:4.1":"Savakam dhutavadanam, ","thi-ap27:4.2":"aggam kittesi nayako; ","thi-ap27:4.3":"Sutva sattahikam danam, ","thi-ap27:4.4":"datva buddhassa tadino. ","thi-ap27:5.1":"Nipacca sirasa pade, ","thi-ap27:5.2":"tam thanamabhipatthayim; ","thi-ap27:5.3":"Sa hasayanto parisam, ","thi-ap27:5.4":"tada hi narapungavo. ","thi-ap27:6.1":"Setthino anukampaya, ","thi-ap27:6.2":"ima gatha abhasatha; ","thi-ap27:6.3":"‘Lacchase patthitam thanam, ","thi-ap27:6.4":"nibbuto hohi puttaka. ","thi-ap27:7.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","thi-ap27:7.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","thi-ap27:7.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","thi-ap27:7.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","thi-ap27:8.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","thi-ap27:8.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","thi-ap27:8.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","thi-ap27:8.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","thi-ap27:9.1":"Tam sutva mudito hutva, ","thi-ap27:9.2":"yavajivam tada jinam; ","thi-ap27:9.3":"Mettacitto paricari, ","thi-ap27:9.4":"paccayehi vinayakam. ","thi-ap27:10.1":"Sasanam jotayitvana, ","thi-ap27:10.2":"so madditva kutitthiye; ","thi-ap27:10.3":"Veneyyam vinayitva ca, ","thi-ap27:10.4":"nibbuto so sasavako. ","thi-ap27:11.1":"Nibbute tamhi lokagge, ","thi-ap27:11.2":"pujanatthaya satthuno; ","thi-ap27:11.3":"Natimitte samanetva, ","thi-ap27:11.4":"saha tehi akarayi. ","thi-ap27:12.1":"Sattayojanikam thupam, ","thi-ap27:12.2":"ubbiddham ratanamayam; ","thi-ap27:12.3":"Jalantam sataramsimva, ","thi-ap27:12.4":"salarajamva phullitam. ","thi-ap27:13.1":"Sattasatasahassani, ","thi-ap27:13.2":"patiyo tattha karayi; ","thi-ap27:13.3":"Nalaggi viya jotanti, ","thi-ap27:13.4":"rataneheva sattahi. ","thi-ap27:14.1":"Gandhatelena puretva, ","thi-ap27:14.2":"dipanujjalayi tahim; ","thi-ap27:14.3":"Pujanatthaya mahesissa, ","thi-ap27:14.4":"sabbabhutanukampino. ","thi-ap27:15.1":"Sattasatasahassani, ","thi-ap27:15.2":"punnakumbhani karayi; ","thi-ap27:15.3":"Rataneheva punnani, ","thi-ap27:15.4":"pujanatthaya mahesino. ","thi-ap27:16.1":"Majjhe atthatthakumbhinam, ","thi-ap27:16.2":"ussita kancanagghiyo; ","thi-ap27:16.3":"Atirocanti vannena, ","thi-ap27:16.4":"saradeva divakaro. ","thi-ap27:17.1":"Catudvaresu sobhanti, ","thi-ap27:17.2":"torana ratanamaya; ","thi-ap27:17.3":"Ussita phalaka ramma, ","thi-ap27:17.4":"sobhanti ratanamaya. ","thi-ap27:18.1":"Virocanti parikkhitta, ","thi-ap27:18.2":"avatamsa sunimmita; ","thi-ap27:18.3":"Ussitani patakani, ","thi-ap27:18.4":"ratanani virocare. ","thi-ap27:19.1":"Surattam sukatam cittam, ","thi-ap27:19.2":"cetiyam ratanamayam; ","thi-ap27:19.3":"Atirocati vannena, ","thi-ap27:19.4":"sasanjhova divakaro. ","thi-ap27:20.1":"Thupassa vediyo tisso, ","thi-ap27:20.2":"haritalena purayi; ","thi-ap27:20.3":"Ekam manosilayekam, ","thi-ap27:20.4":"anjanena ca ekikam. ","thi-ap27:21.1":"Pujam etadisam rammam, ","thi-ap27:21.2":"karetva varavadino; ","thi-ap27:21.3":"Adasi danam sanghassa, ","thi-ap27:21.4":"yavajivam yathabalam. ","thi-ap27:22.1":"Sahava setthina tena, ","thi-ap27:22.2":"tani punnani sabbaso; ","thi-ap27:22.3":"Yavajivam karitvana, ","thi-ap27:22.4":"sahava sugatim gata. ","thi-ap27:23.1":"Sampattiyonubhotvana, ","thi-ap27:23.2":"devatte atha manuse; ","thi-ap27:23.3":"Chaya viya sarirena, ","thi-ap27:23.4":"saha teneva samsarim. ","thi-ap27:24.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","thi-ap27:24.2":"vipassi nama nayako; ","thi-ap27:24.3":"Uppajji carudassano, ","thi-ap27:24.4":"sabbadhammavipassako. ","thi-ap27:25.1":"Tadayam bandhumatiyam, ","thi-ap27:25.2":"brahmano sadhusammato; ","thi-ap27:25.3":"Addho santo gunenapi, ","thi-ap27:25.4":"dhanena ca suduggato. ","thi-ap27:26.1":"Tadapi tassaham asim, ","thi-ap27:26.2":"brahmani samacetasa; ","thi-ap27:26.3":"Kadaci so dijavaro, ","thi-ap27:26.4":"sangamesi mahamunim. ","thi-ap27:27.1":"Nisinnam janakayamhi, ","thi-ap27:27.2":"desentam amatam padam; ","thi-ap27:27.3":"Sutva dhammam pamudito, ","thi-ap27:27.4":"adasi ekasatakam. ","thi-ap27:28.1":"Gharamekena vatthena, ","thi-ap27:28.2":"Gantvanetam sa mabravi; ","thi-ap27:28.3":"‘Anumoda mahapunnam, ","thi-ap27:28.4":"Dinnam buddhassa satakam’. ","thi-ap27:29.1":"Tadaham anjalim katva, ","thi-ap27:29.2":"anumodim supinita; ","thi-ap27:29.3":"‘Sudinno satako sami, ","thi-ap27:29.4":"buddhasetthassa tadino’. ","thi-ap27:30.1":"Sukhito sajjito hutva, ","thi-ap27:30.2":"samsaranto bhavabhave; ","thi-ap27:30.3":"Baranasipure ramme, ","thi-ap27:30.4":"raja asi mahipati. ","thi-ap27:31.1":"Tada tassa mahesiham, ","thi-ap27:31.2":"itthigumbassa uttama; ","thi-ap27:31.3":"Tassati dayita asim, ","thi-ap27:31.4":"pubbasnehena bhattuno. ","thi-ap27:32.1":"Pindaya vicarante te, ","thi-ap27:32.2":"attha paccekanayake; ","thi-ap27:32.3":"Disva pamudito hutva, ","thi-ap27:32.4":"datva pindam maharaham. ","thi-ap27:33.1":"Puno nimantayitvana, ","thi-ap27:33.2":"katva ratanamandapam; ","thi-ap27:33.3":"Kammarehi katam pattam, ","thi-ap27:33.4":"sovannam vata tattakam. ","thi-ap27:34.1":"Samanetvana te sabbe, ","thi-ap27:34.2":"tesam danamadasi so; ","thi-ap27:34.3":"Sonnasane pavitthanam, ","thi-ap27:34.4":"pasanno sehi panibhi. ","thi-ap27:35.1":"Tampi danam sahadasim, ","thi-ap27:35.2":"kasirajenaham tada; ","thi-ap27:35.3":"Punaham baranasiyam, ","thi-ap27:35.4":"jata kasikagamake. ","thi-ap27:36.1":"Kutumbikakule phite, ","thi-ap27:36.2":"sukhito so sabhatuko; ","thi-ap27:36.3":"Jetthassa bhatuno jaya, ","thi-ap27:36.4":"ahosim supatibbata. ","thi-ap27:37.1":"Paccekabuddham disvana, ","thi-ap27:37.2":"kaniyassa mama bhattuno; ","thi-ap27:37.3":"Bhagannam tassa datvana, ","thi-ap27:37.4":"agate tamhi pavadim. ","thi-ap27:38.1":"Nabhinandittha so danam, ","thi-ap27:38.2":"tato tassa adasaham; ","thi-ap27:38.3":"Ukha aniya tam annam, ","thi-ap27:38.4":"puno tasseva so ada. ","thi-ap27:39.1":"Tadannam chaddayitvana, ","thi-ap27:39.2":"duttha buddhassaham tada; ","thi-ap27:39.3":"Pattam kalalapunnam tam, ","thi-ap27:39.4":"adasim tassa tadino. ","thi-ap27:40.1":"Dane ca gahane ceva, ","thi-ap27:40.2":"apace padusepi ca; ","thi-ap27:40.3":"Samacittamukham disva, ","thi-ap27:40.4":"tadaham samvijim bhusam. ","thi-ap27:41.1":"Puno pattam gahetvana, ","thi-ap27:41.2":"sodhayitva sugandhina; ","thi-ap27:41.3":"Pasannacitta puretva, ","thi-ap27:41.4":"saghatam sakkaram adam. ","thi-ap27:42.1":"Yattha yatthupapajjami, ","thi-ap27:42.2":"surupa homi danato; ","thi-ap27:42.3":"Buddhassa apakarena, ","thi-ap27:42.4":"duggandha vadanena ca. ","thi-ap27:43.1":"Puna kassapavirassa, ","thi-ap27:43.2":"nidhayantamhi cetiye; ","thi-ap27:43.3":"Sovannam itthakam varam, ","thi-ap27:43.4":"adasim mudita aham. ","thi-ap27:44.1":"Catujjatena gandhena, ","thi-ap27:44.2":"nicayitva tamitthakam; ","thi-ap27:44.3":"Mutta duggandhadosamha, ","thi-ap27:44.4":"sabbangasusamagata. ","thi-ap27:45.1":"Sattapatisahassani, ","thi-ap27:45.2":"rataneheva sattahi; ","thi-ap27:45.3":"Karetva ghatapurani, ","thi-ap27:45.4":"vattini ca sahassaso. ","thi-ap27:46.1":"Pakkhipitva padipetva, ","thi-ap27:46.2":"thapayim sattapantiyo; ","thi-ap27:46.3":"Pujanattham lokanathassa, ","thi-ap27:46.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","thi-ap27:47.1":"Tadapi tamhi punnamhi, ","thi-ap27:47.2":"bhaginiham visesato; ","thi-ap27:47.3":"Puna kasisu sanjato, ","thi-ap27:47.4":"sumitto iti vissuto. ","thi-ap27:48.1":"Tassaham bhariya asim, ","thi-ap27:48.2":"sukhita sajjita piya; ","thi-ap27:48.3":"Tada paccekamunino, ","thi-ap27:48.4":"adasim ghanavethanam. ","thi-ap27:49.1":"Tassapi bhagini asim, ","thi-ap27:49.2":"moditva danamuttamam; ","thi-ap27:49.3":"Punapi kasiratthamhi, ","thi-ap27:49.4":"jato koliyajatiya. ","thi-ap27:50.1":"Tada koliyaputtanam, ","thi-ap27:50.2":"satehi saha pancahi; ","thi-ap27:50.3":"Pancapaccekabuddhanam, ","thi-ap27:50.4":"satani samupatthahi. ","thi-ap27:51.1":"Temasam tappayitvana, ","thi-ap27:51.2":"adasi ca ticivaram; ","thi-ap27:51.3":"Jaya tassa tada asim, ","thi-ap27:51.4":"punnakammapathanuga. ","thi-ap27:52.1":"Tato cuto ahu raja, ","thi-ap27:52.2":"nando nama mahayaso; ","thi-ap27:52.3":"Tassapi mahesi asim, ","thi-ap27:52.4":"sabbakamasamiddhini. ","thi-ap27:53.1":"Tada raja bhavitvana, ","thi-ap27:53.2":"brahmadatto mahipati; ","thi-ap27:53.3":"Padumavatiputtanam, ","thi-ap27:53.4":"paccekamuninam tada. ","thi-ap27:54.1":"Satani pancanunani, ","thi-ap27:54.2":"yavajivam upatthahim; ","thi-ap27:54.3":"Rajuyyane nivasetva, ","thi-ap27:54.4":"nibbutani ca pujayim. ","thi-ap27:55.1":"Cetiyani ca karetva, ","thi-ap27:55.2":"pabbajitva ubho mayam; ","thi-ap27:55.3":"Bhavetva appamannayo, ","thi-ap27:55.4":"brahmalokam agamhase. ","thi-ap27:56.1":"Tato cuto mahatitthe, ","thi-ap27:56.2":"sujato pipphalayano; ","thi-ap27:56.3":"Mata sumanadeviti, ","thi-ap27:56.4":"kosigotto dijo pita. ","thi-ap27:57.1":"Aham madde janapade, ","thi-ap27:57.2":"sakalaya puruttame; ","thi-ap27:57.3":"Kappilassa dijassasim, ","thi-ap27:57.4":"dhita mata sucimati. ","thi-ap27:58.1":"Ghanakancanabimbena, ","thi-ap27:58.2":"nimminitvana mam pita; ","thi-ap27:58.3":"Ada kassapadhirassa, ","thi-ap27:58.4":"kamehi vajjitassamam. ","thi-ap27:59.1":"Kadaci so karuniko, ","thi-ap27:59.2":"gantva kammantapekkhako; ","thi-ap27:59.3":"Kakadikehi khajjante, ","thi-ap27:59.4":"pane disvana samviji. ","thi-ap27:60.1":"Gharevaham tile jate, ","thi-ap27:60.2":"disvanatapatapane; ","thi-ap27:60.3":"Kimi kakehi khajjante, ","thi-ap27:60.4":"samvegamalabhim tada. ","thi-ap27:61.1":"Tada so pabbaji dhiro, ","thi-ap27:61.2":"aham tamanupabbajim; ","thi-ap27:61.3":"Pancavassani nivasim, ","thi-ap27:61.4":"paribbajavate aham. ","thi-ap27:62.1":"Yada pabbajita asi, ","thi-ap27:62.2":"gotami jinaposika; ","thi-ap27:62.3":"Tadaham tamupagantva, ","thi-ap27:62.4":"buddhena anusasita. ","thi-ap27:63.1":"Na cireneva kalena, ","thi-ap27:63.2":"arahattamapapunim; ","thi-ap27:63.3":"Aho kalyanamittattam, ","thi-ap27:63.4":"kassapassa sirimato. ","thi-ap27:64.1":"Suto buddhassa dayado, ","thi-ap27:64.2":"kassapo susamahito; ","thi-ap27:64.3":"Pubbenivasam yo vedi, ","thi-ap27:64.4":"saggapayanca passati. ","thi-ap27:65.1":"Atho jatikkhayam patto, ","thi-ap27:65.2":"abhinnavosito muni; ","thi-ap27:65.3":"Etahi tihi vijjahi, ","thi-ap27:65.4":"tevijjo hoti brahmano. ","thi-ap27:66.1":"Tatheva bhaddakapilani, ","thi-ap27:66.2":"tevijja maccuhayini; ","thi-ap27:66.3":"Dhareti antimam deham, ","thi-ap27:66.4":"jitva maram savahanam. ","thi-ap27:67.1":"Disva adinavam loke, ","thi-ap27:67.2":"ubho pabbajita mayam; ","thi-ap27:67.3":"Tyamha khinasava danta, ","thi-ap27:67.4":"sitibhutamha nibbuta. ","thi-ap27:68.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap27:68.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap27:68.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap27:69.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap27:69.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap27:69.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap27:70.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap27:70.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap27:70.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap27:71.1":"Ittham sudam bhaddakapilani bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap27:72.1":"Bhaddakapilanitheriyapadanam sattamam. "}